metadata.name: mrs grimez
metadata.description:
a portrait
it contains what you think and feel as you sink to the bottom
when you feel like you're sinking to the bottom of the ocean trying to escape from yourself, you're wrapped up
when the things you take to get rid of your thoughts start to take effect one by one, you don't feel like yourself anymore, but you are just as much and you exist
you're surrounded by beings at the bottom of the ocean, and you're floating
everything is lighter now
everything is blurry now
calm down
close your eyes
let yourself flow

2160x1620 pixels
